sentences: Anatoli Vasilyevich Ivanov (Russian: Анато́лий Васи́льевич Ивано́в; June 26, 1934 – April 2, 2012) was a Russian solo-timpanist, percussionist with the Saint Petersburg Philharmonic Orchestra, book author and People's Artist of Russia (1997).
A tribute concert was held on at Mariinsky Theatre on 12 April 2016.
